body_html:
One way to narrow down this issue is to look at run_metadata.step_stats, to
see if the "Unknown" are also seen there, in which case it's problem with
tracing. Otherwise it's a problem in Timeline generation.

On Mon, Aug 15, 2016 at 12:33 PM, Mazecreator notifications@github.com
wrote:

Just a ping to keep this alive. I can upload something if that speeds up
the answer. Still very suspicious that MatMul seems to be the only Op on
the GPU I found that has these 2 additional MatMul's spawned with the
"undefined" inputs.
